data.description: Wonderful ranch home in popular Chestnut Hill Farms. This home sits both on a quiet street and inside corner. A huge kitchen for entertaining. The large living room has a beautiful bricked fireplace with gas logs. Both the living room and kitchen open up to a lovely sunroom that has fully conditioned air.  First floor laundry, 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms. Front bedroom is currently being used as an office. 150 amp electrical panel, newer Lennox furnace, humidifier, digital thermostat and HWH. All but 2 file cabinets stay for great additional storage. Close to expressways, schools, recreation, and Village of Clarkston. Clarkston Community Schools. B.A.T.V.A.I.
